rily served Departments of Transportation and municipal agencies in roles such as resident engineer and construction project manager. His expertise spans corporate and construction management, infrastructure planning, development and design, and construction surveying, giving him a comprehensive understanding of the full project lifecycle.<\/p><p>In addition to his professional work, Hildebranski is an adjunct instructor at Joliet Junior College, where he teaches construction layout, sharing his field knowledge with the next generation of engineers. He also hosts The Construction Engineering Show Podcast and manages a companion website, both dedicated to advancing the skills and insights of civil and construction engineering professionals.<\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":"","elType":"section"}],"settings":{"width":{"unit":"px","size":1000,"sizes":[]},"entrance_animation":"fadeIn","exit_animation":"fadeIn","entrance_animation_duration":{"unit":"px","size":"0.5","sizes":[]},"overlay_background_color":"#FFFAF5CC","close_button_color":"#0F1319","close_button_hover_color":"#5659C7","width_tablet":{"unit":"px","size":"720","sizes":[]},"__globals__":{"overlay_background_color":"","close_button_color":"","close_button_hover_color":""}},"metadata":{"disable_sitewide_popup":""},"display_settings":{"triggers":{"click":"yes","click_times":1},"timing":{"devices":"yes","devices_devices":["desktop","mobile","mobile_extra","tablet","tablet_extra","laptop","widescreen"]}}}